    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2 with documented justification. Output comparison achieves MRL 3 performance (18% maximum deviation vs. 30% threshold). RH < 1 criterion satisfied across all five CPB operating conditions. The assessment team confirms that all project requirements identified in the V&V planning documentation have been addressed through the factor assessments and supporting evidence. The credibility package is accepted as sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision for the Class II CPB device.",
